description:
Expand your track list with the Legendary Hits Song Pack! You need the full game Let's Sing Country to use this DLC. Includes hit songs:
• Gloria Gaynor "I Will Survive"
• Vanessa Carlton "A Thousand Miles"
• The Cure "Boys Don't Cry"
• Lilly Allen "The Fear"
• Lady Gaga "Bad Romance"
name: Let's Sing - Legendary Hits Song Pack
